# ğŸ“Š Customer Pick-Up Analytics (CPU) â€“ Power BI Project

This repository showcases a **Customer Pick-Up (CPU) analytics solution** built using **Power BI, SQL, and Excel/Power Query**.  
The goal of this project is to monitor and improve **CPU compliance, response time, and pending orders** across warehouses, helping operations teams make **data-driven decisions**.

---

## ğŸ¯ Project Overview

The CPU dashboard focuses on:

- **CPU Compliance %** â€“ How many CPU orders meet the check-in/response SLA.
- **Customer Response Time** â€“ Time between customer check-in and first response.
- **Pending CPU Orders** â€“ Orders that are ready/past due but not yet completed.
- **Warehouse-Level Performance** â€“ Comparing CPU metrics across different branches.
- **Daily Trends** â€“ Tracking performance over time for continuous improvement.

This project reflects how I work with **data, stakeholders, and operations teams** to design useful dashboards.

